New York Synagogue Bomb Plotters Should Get Life Sentences, U.S. Says

-- B y   E d v a r d   P e t t e r s s o n
-- 
2011-06-08T22:59:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-08/new-york-synagogue-bomb-plotters-should-get-life-sentences-u-s-says.html
Federal prosecutors In  New York  asked
that four men convicted in a foiled plot to bomb synagogues and
fire heat-seeking missiles at military planes be sentenced to
life imprisonment.  To contact the reporter on this story:
